p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Adds a `equals null` filter clause onto a query
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92: Adds a `equals null` predicate to the given query. This predicate indicates to the query to filter out the objects whose the specified property has no value (equals `null`).
The query to which the equals null filter must be added
The query including the `equals null` filter
The property used by the filter to execute the predicate to check if that property has a value or not.
